metadata.name: Solitude
metadata.description:
There are very few places that force stops my train of thoughts. Ease your pain and talk to yourself. One thing is assured at least someone is listening. Get the answer you want. 
 
Amidst the chaos, there comes a moment when you find yourself and realise, “where have you been lately?” Do you also wonder where you have been lately?

Love thyself. Just like this frame.
